<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Beanster</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to Beanster!</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
      <% if (user) { %>
        <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
        <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/auth/google">Login with Google</a>
      <% } %>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main>
    <h2>About Beanster</h2>
    <p>
      Beanster is an exclusive platform designed to provide a seamless and secure experience for authorized users. Our app allows manually verified users to integrate their content with TikTok securely and efficiently. We prioritize your privacy and security while offering top-notch functionality.
    </p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Exclusive Access:</strong> Only users who have been manually verified by us can use the app.</li>
      <li><strong>Secure OAuth Registration:</strong> We utilize OAuth for secure user authentication and registration.</li>
      <li><strong>Seamless Integration:</strong> Effortlessly integrate your content with TikTok while maintaining control over your data.</li>
      <li><strong>User Privacy:</strong> We are committed to protecting your personal information. Read our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> to learn more.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Getting Started</h2>
    <p>
      To begin using Beanster, please <a href="/auth/google">Login with Google</a> using our secure OAuth process.
    </p>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Beanster</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
